snippet.title: FIRST STAR DOWN - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
FIRST STAR DOWN is an enigmatic journey that follows Natalie Haines as she joins a deep-space research project to determine the origins of a mysterious signal. 

Resealing on Steam in 2020. 
Available to wishlist on Steam at http://www.firststardown.com 


A game by PROJECTaroid http://www.projectaroid.com 

Narration by Lana Lux https://www.twitch.tv/lana_lux
